fullName: Retrieve a list of cat breeds using the Cat Fact API: Successfully get a list of cat breeds

steps.name: Given the Cat Fact API is available
When I make a GET request to the "/breeds" endpoint
Then the response status code should be 200
And the response should contain a list of cat breeds
And each breed object should have the following fields
And the response should have a "Content-Type" header with value "application/json"
And the list of breeds should not be empty
And the limit parameter should be set to 10 and should limit the number of returned breeds to 10
